[2] 安萊絲替《格雷的五十道陰影》進行的辯護如下：「我全心相信女性擁有情慾幻想的權利。我支持女人書寫並閱讀情慾幻想。而我反對任何試圖規訓或淨化女人（與男人）情慾幻想的嘗試。」（I believe completely in the right of women to their own sexual fantasies. I believe in their right to write and read sexual fantasies, and I will always defend them (and men) against efforts to politicize or sanitize or patrol their sexual fantasies.）


[3] 這篇文章原先發表於《新聞週刊》（Newsweek），而後收入凱蒂洛菲的文集《邋遢頌》（In Praise of Messy Lives）。請見Roiphe. In Praise of Messy Lives. New York: The Dial Press, 2012.


[4] Roiphe. The Morning After: Sex, Fear and Feminism. New York: Back Bay Books, 1993.


[5] 關於盧本對於八〇年代女性主義性論戰的反思，以及她寫出經典的〈再思性〉一文以後所受到的各種批評，請見Rubin. “Blood under the Bridge: Reflections on ‘Thinking Sex.’” Deviations: A Gayle Rubin Reader. Durham: Duke UP, 2011. 194-223.


[6] 這篇文章原先發表於同志雜誌《主張》（The Advocate）中，後收入卡利菲亞的文集《公共性：性激進文化》（Public Sex: The Culture of Radical Sex）中。請見 Califia. Public Sex: The Culture of Radical Sex. San Francisco: Cleis P, 1994. 158-67.


[7] Rubin. “Thinking Sex.” Pleasure and Danger: Exploring Female Sexuality. Ed. Carole S. Vance. Boston: Routledge & Kegan Paul, 1984. 267-319.


[8] 巴納德性會議在女性主義性論戰史上扮演了承上啟下的關鍵性角色。在這場會議後，性論戰持續蔓延。1986年由五學院女性研究計畫（Five College Women’s Studies Project）舉辦的「女性主義、性慾與權力」（Feminism, Sexuality, and Power）研討會，引爆了另一波的女性主義論戰。1993年，一群美國女性主義學者受邀前往澳洲國立大學（Australian National University）的人文研究中心發表，同樣受到澳洲基進女性主義者的抨擊。盧本形容五學院研討會與澳洲國立大學的性論戰就像是巴納德性會議的「第二幕」與「第三幕」。


[9] Vance, ed. Pleasure and Danger: Exploring Female Sexuality. Boston: Routledge & Kegan Paul, 1984.


[10] Damsky, ed. Sex and Single Girls: Straight and Queer Women on Sexuality. Berkeley: Seal Press, 2000.


[11] Brown, Helen Gurley. Sex and the Single Girl. New York: Bernard Geis Associates, 1964.


[12] Johnson, Merri Lisa, ed. Jane Sexes It Up: True Confessions of Feminist Desire. Berkeley: Seal Press, 2002.


[13] Henry. Not My Mother’s Sister: Generational Conflict and Third-Wave Feminism. Bloomington and Indianapolis: Indiana UP, 2004.






